commit.message: Implement Table View with automatic extraction for e-commerce domain and professor homepage
Create a new tab to display the grid. Editing the grid is possible but not integrated yet: https://editor.datatables.net/examples/inline-editing/simple.html
Use data table instead of handsome table. See some instances of adding the library multiple time (in background.js and in manifest). Just a caution, not harmful yet.
